<note n="0123001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123001">Duḷudesa 楞伽島之外，恐是南印度之一地方。</note>
<note n="0123002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123002">敘事羅瑪耶那之主人公。</note>
<note n="0123003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123003">Ayojjhā skt. Ayodhyā 阿輸陀國。羅馬王與西多妃所住之都。</note>
<note n="0123004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123004">王女之名利羅瓦提 Līlāvatī。</note>
</p>
